  "text": [
    "It's neither red",
    "nor sweet.",
    "It doesn't melt",
    "or turn over,",
    "break or harden,",
    "so it can't feel",
    "pain,",
    "yearning,",
    "regret.",
    "It doesn't have",
    "a tip to spin on,",
    "it isn't even",
    "shapely\u2014",
    "just a thick clutch",
    "of muscle,",
    "lopsided,",
    "mute. Still,",
    "I feel it inside",
    "its cage sounding",
    "a dull tattoo:",
    "\u2014",
    "but I can't open it:",
    "there's no key.",
    "I can't wear it",
    "on my sleeve,",
    "or tell you from",
    "the bottom of it",
    "how I feel. Here,",
    "it's all yours, now\u2014",
    "but you'll have",
    "to take me,",
    "too."
  ],
  "title": "Heart to Heart",
  "year": ""
}